column2: SELECT    p.ra, p.dec, p.modelmag_z - p.extinction_z as magModel_z_DR7, p.fibermag_z - p.extinction_z as magFiber_z_DR7    INTO   myDB.mags_DR1#    FROM   DR1#.PhotoObj as d, DR7.PhoObj as s, DR1#.SpecObj as sd, DR7.SpecObj as ss    WHERE   sd.z <= # AND sd.z >= # AND   sd.plate = ss.plate AND sd.mjd = ss.mjd AND sd.fiberid = ss.fiberid AND   d.bestObjID = sd.bestObjID AND   s.bestObjID = ss.bestObjID
